 />\n如果係阿婆阿叔 咪慢慢講囉 <br />\n後生仔囡 咪&quot;3號餐可樂喺度食&quot;咁<br />\n<br />\n不過其實講得快 頂盡多幾秒 <br />\n一陣條友聽錯 又落錯單<br />\n到時用多成幾分鐘去換比你<br />\n咁就無謂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽啲做過老麥嘅朋友講<br />\n就算有幾多人喺後面排<br />\n都要Double confirm個客要乜<br />\n<br />\n同埋莫講話老麥<br />\n茶記 大排檔 什至 高級餐廳嘅待應都會咁做<br />\n都係一句<br />\n落錯單 就無謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f617cc4f2a9d43bc81e86fb62af13f432cca159d","tid":286942,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d77175f9a1745b49d93d5ec877080379fe40bcc8","tid":286942,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"其實岩岩俾阿姐話 ： <span style=\"color: red;\">講得好</span>"},{"pid":"bbc0ca0acc52fe0000343d502bead514bed5c9af","tid":286942,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"入機流程順序有冇人知？"},{"pid":"2b0c691bb4cf791d35c553e605231aaafb4acc1a","tid":286942,"uid":115252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想要豬柳蛋漢堡仲要麥樂雞餐</blockquote><br />\n我想要脆辣雞腿包餐<br />\n加<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">超大</span>魚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">特大</span>柳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超大</span>包"},{"pid":"d00b76b9380915867e3d18e0082ae4a25e7c945f","tid":286942,"uid":72275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T21:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想要豬柳蛋漢堡仲要麥樂雞餐</blockquote><br />\n我想要脆辣雞腿包餐<br />\n加<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">超大</span>魚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">特大</span>柳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超大</span>包</blockquote><br />\nRun Egg"}]}